{
  "stem": "15396.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so was Beamish, and so were Jean [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "These were wonderful people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was lucky to know people like that, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was lucky to know some of these Jewish because we didn't know who they were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were numbers to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of them didn't even have names, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We just called them 'that man over in the such-and-such a [NON-ENGLISH].' Yeah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you find it difficult when you asked or offered to hide people for you and help you?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You had to go about it very discretely.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you had to do sometimes-- sometimes you had to make two or three meetings with these people before you could really determine if they would be trustworthy.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a good way to do it would be to let slip something that as they could be interpreted as pro-Nazi and see how they reacted.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then you had to rush and straighten that out in a hurry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you make a-- Fry told us how to do this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I think Jean [INAUDIBLE] told us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He would teach you just like a dialogue coach, you know, and drop something that could mean that you were a collaborator.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then you'd see their reaction, then you had to quickly say, hm, good, your reaction was perfect.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then that put them at ease then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then you knew that they were--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--more or less on your side of the fence.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were A lot of tricks that you could find out, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The gangsters, all of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as I say, there was one-- one who we ran a big charge account with.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A big one.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we knew more or less where we shouldn't go.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
